@NODE EVALUATION_LIMITS
  EVALUATION LIMITS

    The evaluation version of HypAss is limited in some rare points,
     because you should have an additional reason to register:

        Source size:            unlimited
        Include size:           unlimited
        Include files:          unlimited
        Include nesting levels: unlimited

        Macro size:             unlimited
        Macros:                 unlimited     in LOWMEM mode all macros
        Macro nesting levels:   unlimited     must fit in 32K heap!

        Labels + symbols:       unlimited
        Forward references:     unlimited

        Object size:            unlimited    (if supported by object format)

    The term 'unlimited' means not especially limited by HypAss, but the
    limits of you memory and storage medium space can't be changed by HypAss
    for reasons you should normally know, if you are a programmer! ;-)

  LATEST NEWS:

    I have decided not to cripple hypass in any way, at least in this release.


